    </div>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">Framework connection: The Natural Framework pipeline's composition with contracts is graded COMP. Each stage carries an effect grade that composes through the handshake. (<a href="https://june.kim/the-handshake"><img src="/reading/jk.png" alt="jk" style="display:inline;height:1em;vertical-align:-0.1em;margin-right:0.2em;"/>The Handshake</a>, <a href="https://june.kim/ambient-category"><img src="/reading/jk.png" alt="jk" style="display:inline;height:1em;vertical-align:-0.1em;margin-right:0.2em;"/>Ambient Category</a>)</p>

